Stocks Retreat After Swinging Between Gains and Losses in London Trading

-- B y   S a r a h   J o n e s
-- 
2011-09-23T09:54:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/stocks-retreat-after-swinging-between-gains-and-losses-in-london-trading.html
U.K. stocks erased gains, sending
the FTSE 100 Index down 0.4 percent to 5,024.95 at 10:52 a.m. in
 London . The gauge, which earlier rallied as much as 1.3 percent,
has swung between gains and losses at least five times today
after slumping 4.7 percent yesterday.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
